<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email-Safe Classified Button (Wider & Longer)</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
        background: #f0f0f0;
      }

      .preview {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: white;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }

      .code-section {
        background: #1a1a1a;
        color: #00ff00;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 16px;
        overflow-x: auto;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .code-section h3 {
        color: #ab0000;
        margin-top: 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="preview">

      <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; background: #000000; border: 4px solid #ab0000;">
        <tr>
          <td style="background: #ab0000; color: white; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 25px; letter-spacing: 4px;">
            ★ ★ TOP SECRET - CLASSIFIED ★ ★
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="background: #ab0000; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 2px;">
            CONFIDENTIAL - AUTHORIZED PERSONNEL ONLY
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="background: #1a1a1a; color: #ffffff; padding: 60px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.9;">
            <div style="color: #ffff00; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center; font-size: 24px;">
              ⚠️ DO NOT FORWARD THIS MESSAGE, ${Recipient.FIRST_NAME} ⚠️
            </div>
            <p style="margin: 30px 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 20px;">
              <strong>This is urgent.</strong> Schumer and the Dems are flooding red states with dark money to block Trump. I need trusted allies only to see this private message I wrote to fight back:
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 30px 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 20px;">
              PRIVATE MESSAGE FROM: Ryan Zinke<br>
              SUBJECT: ██████████████████<br>
              PRIORITY: <span style="color: #ab0000; font-weight: bold;">IMMEDIATE ACTION REQUIRED</span>
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 30px 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 20px;">
              You're seeing this because I trust you to keep it quiet. Don't break that trust.
            </p>
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 50px 0;">
              <a href="https://secure.winred.com/schmitt-for-senate/2026-dems-playbook" style="background: #ab0000; color: white; padding: 28px 60px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; text-decoration: none; border: 3px solid #ffffff; display: inline-block;">
                🔒 READ MY PRIVATE MESSAGE NOW
              </a>
            </div>
            <div style="color: #ffff00; font-size: 18px; text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; font-weight: bold;">
              ⚠️ FOR AUTHORIZED EYES ONLY ⚠️<br>
              MESSAGE EXPIRES IN 24 HOURS
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="background: #ab0000; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;">
            CLASSIFIED DOCUMENT - HANDLE WITH EXTREME CARE
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </body>

</html>
